===Spell Casting AI===

Monsters with spell abilities have a 25% (64/256) chance to cast instead of attacking each turn.

'''Enemy Spell Effects:'''
* '''HURT''': Deals 2-7 damage to player
* '''HURTMORE''': Deals 15-23 damage to player
* '''HEAL''': Restores 7-23 HP to self
* '''HEALMORE''': Restores 75-100 HP to self
* '''SLEEP''': 50% - (PlayerLevel × 2) chance to put player to sleep (min 12.5%)
* '''STOPSPELL''': Blocks player from casting spells for 2-5 turns
* '''Breath Attack''': High damage fire/ice breath (25-60 damage)

===Special AI: Dragonlord===

'''Form 1 (Human):'''
* 50% chance: Cast HURTMORE (15-23 damage)
* 25% chance: Cast HURT (2-7 damage)
* 25% chance: Physical attack

'''Form 2 (Dragon):'''
* Turn 1: Always use Breath Attack (devastating damage)
* HP > 50%: 50% Breath Attack, 50% Physical Attack
* HP ≤ 50%: 75% HEALMORE (75-100 HP), 25% Physical Attack

